{"tid":61604,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[救命］開機自動熄又再開又熄，無限loop","createTime":"2016-12-31T10:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T12:08:37.000Z","uid":4324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3eb1ddcc3d7628658d73243957d108a0bcfbc242","tid":61604,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T10:57:55.000Z","msg":"Desktop砌機黎，開機時：<br />\n會著燈<br />\n風扇會郁<br />\n之後熄，然後再開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCheck左底版啲粒粒冇爆到（係，我電腦常識好基本）<br />\n電源好正常，都試過再插<br />\n<br />\n上網睇話用火酒抹下ram或其他啲銅片，仲有咩方法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3372e61a9fdaf0779b8e33acdbc1632b0068a69","tid":61604,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T11:04:15.000Z","msg":"底板入面啲線鬆咗？"},{"pid":"b24aef41e74c387a14a9b04a6c765fbd5458abe6","tid":61604,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>底板入面啲線鬆咗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCheck左又冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾一日先跪底"},{"pid":"68086e1dc58c5d8008db12d8700a70f4b68c01be","tid":61604,"uid":31873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"死windows 或者HD"},{"pid":"7137f1ae29d84474484f8cbf9d395b2c22a8cdc1","tid":61604,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T11:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死windows 或者HD</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死兩隻有咩救決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4f4aea22eada9af29b6e0545560e0fcbb13508","tid":61604,"uid":31873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T11:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><b